item.title: By: Matt Whites
item.dc:creator: Matt Whites
item.description: <p>Hi, my name is not Matt White. But it is Matt Whites. So when I did a search on my name I found your title "Matt Whites of the world unite." My name is pronouced Whytus. But I don't know the history of my name so it could be just another take on the White last name. Every time I searched it I find sites that say it is Scotish.</p>
item.content:encoded: Hi, my name is not Matt White. But it is Matt Whites. So when I did a search on my name I found your title “Matt Whites of the world unite.” My name is pronouced Whytus. But I don’t know the history of my name so it could be just another take on the White last name. Every time I searched it I find sites that say it is Scotish.

item.content:encoded:
I’ve just run across a couple more Matt White blogs. It looks like 11tmr is still the only U.K Matt White blog (maybe even the only E.U. and Commonwealth Matt White blog).

Thanks the mention, by the way.

Thank you, Mum, for that “looks young” comment.
